import { Typography } from '@mui/material'
import { Box } from '@mui/system'
import React from 'react'
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'
import HomeBanner from '../../Components/Banner/HomeBanner'
import ProjectListing from '../../Components/Listing/ProjectListing'
import PropertyListing from '../../Components/Listing/PropertyListing'

const Home = () => {
  return (
    <Box p={3} mt={2}>
      <Typography variant='h5' component='div' fontWeight={600}>
        Discover New Projects
      </Typography>
      <Typography variant='subtitle1' style={{textDecoration:'none'}}>
        <Link to='/project'  style={{textDecoration:'none' , fontSize:'13px'}}>
          View All listing project
        </Link>
      </Typography>
      
      <ProjectListing />
       
       <HomeBanner />

       <PropertyListing />
    </Box>
  )
}

export default Home
